- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a new learning framework for jointly optimizing visual representation and dynamics models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses using model-based planning to solve challenging manipulation tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper discusses learning dynamics models for deformable objects.
